58
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,360
Well,

59
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,040
don't disappoint me again.

60
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,200
Otherwise,

61
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,780
