62
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,720
When we signed the contract,

63
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,380
I had a bad feeling about this.

64
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,720
I never expected that

65
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,520
compared to Director Zhong,

66
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,380
I was ultimately one move behind.

67
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:09,580
