68
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,580
However, integrity is the foundation of business.

69
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,840
That's also why

70
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,970
I wanted to cooperate with Long Group.

71
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,440
