75
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,520
Of course,

76
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:33,560
if I find out who's pulling strings behind the scenes,

77
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,159
I won't let them off the hook.

78
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,440
Your company's affairs

79
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,440
are none of my business

80
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,240
and I have no right to interfere.

81
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:43,840
Anyway,

82
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,760
I hope Director Long will make the payment as agreed.

83
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:49,690
Let's not disturb Director Long's work any further.

84
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:54,460
I hope you find the mastermind behind this soon.

85
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,320
What is it now?

86
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,200
Mr.

87
