Director,

88
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,840
someone named Li Yiran from Red Sail Capital wants to see you.

89
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,520
Let her in.

90
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,040
Haotian.

91
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,200
