about the contract with Hengxin Group

101
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,200
and the penalty fees?

102
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,730
That amount of money

103
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,260
is something I can afford.

104
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:46,120
That amount?

105
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,180
Do you even know how much it is?

106
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,200
I do.

107
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,040
Haotian.

108
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,280
Didn't I tell you before?

109
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:59,160
Eight years ago, I left you

110
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,380
