115
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,320
To be honest,

116
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,640
I am now

117
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,840
the heir to Red Sail Capital.

118
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:22,640
Red Sail Capital?

119
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,720
I know you might not believe me

120
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,960
but what I'm saying

121
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,320
is the truth.

122
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:33,720
Children.

123
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:37,570
Today I'm here representing the company to visit you all

124
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,700
please don't be shy

125
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,240
we're all old friends now.

126
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,760
May I relax a bit?

127
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,440
Yes.

128
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:46,520
If you have anything you want to do in the future

129
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:48,440
or any wishes you want to fulfill

130
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,320
just tell Director Wang

131
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,560
and I'll help make them come true.

132
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,440
Okay?

133
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:55,000
Okay.

134
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,560
Mr. Li.

135
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,920
Thank you for all these years

136
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,240
of donations to our orphanage

137
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,920
I thank you again on behalf of everyone.

138
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,960
Oh, Director Wang, you're too kind

139
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:08,080
being able to do something for these children

140
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,520
is my greatest honor.

141
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,920
Mr. Li, you're too modest

142
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,780
this is all what I should be doing.

143
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,480
Very good, children.

144
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,000
Come.

145
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:16,730
Come, Yiran.

146
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:18,680
Come, Yiran.

147
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:19,540
Come over here.

148
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,680
Mr. Li

149
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,810
let me introduce you

150
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,120
this is Li Yiran

151
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,780
she's eighteen this year.

152
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,000
This child

153
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,680
has been smart and sensible since she was little

154
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:34,480
and often helps us take care of the other children.

155
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:36,880
Every time she sees you doing charity work

156
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:37,920
Yiran says

157
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,920
that when she grows up, she wants to be like you

158
00:11:39,920 --> 00:11:40,600
using her own abilities

159
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,600
to help others.

160
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,320
However

161
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,320
our orphanage

162
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:47,320
