163
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,280
So I'd like to introduce her to you

164
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,920
so she can learn from you

165
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:52,280
and gain some experience.

166
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,680
If she becomes successful in the future

167
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:54,320
I believe

168
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:57,380
