177
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:18,360
Our Long family needs someone of equal status

178
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,020
someone who can help Haotian.

179
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,360
And you?

180
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,000
You can't do anything.

181
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:26,720
I'm willing

182
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,840
I want to be like you

183
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,480
able to help more people.

184
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:33,620
It's very good that you think this way

185
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,320
but you must remember

186
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,480
